CustomField.description: This field determines the number of bits we use for our hash key. This is directly related to how much storage space is used for the scenario and is auto calculated by the key builder. Please do not change this without contacting support.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: This field determines the number of bits we use for our hash key and is automatically calculated by the key builder. Please do not change this without contacting support.
CustomField.label: Hash Key Bits
